headline: DEWALT速 Expands Its Lineup of Outdoor Power Equipment Solutions to Tackle the Most Demanding Landscaping Jobs
summary: Eighty-one percent (81%) of Americans have a lawn to maintain, according to a survey from the National Association of Landscape Professionals (NALP), which they also cite as one of the most important features of their home.
